Usage: unspecifyBlackBox [-help] [-keepPtn] { -cell <string> | -all  }

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-all               # Selects all blackboxes for unspecification.
                   # (bool, optional)
-cell <string>     # Selects an individual blackbox for unspecification. You
                   # can use wildcards (*?) with this parameter.
                   # (string, optional)
-keepPtn           # Preserves the partition information.It is used only if
                   # blackbox is placed inside core area and is defined as a
                   # module in the netlist.  (bool, optional)